00:33:09.740 --> 00:33:12.440
OK, it's not just
how we mellow--

00:33:12.440 --> 00:33:16.280
like we're the collateral
damage in a family when

00:33:16.280 --> 00:33:17.866
people are working this hard.

00:33:17.866 --> 00:33:19.490
So those are a couple
of simple things,

00:33:19.490 --> 00:33:22.860
but I would tell you that
Commonwealth Club-- man,

